BUT TRUST
IS NOT AN ARGUMENT

41:35.761 --> 41:36.795
THAT CAN BE WON OR LOST.

41:36.828 --> 41:42.701
MAYBE I JUST HAVE TO SUSPEND
MY CYNICISM AND BELIEVE.

41:44.770 --> 41:47.606
MAYBE IT'S TIME
I TOOK A LEAP OF FAITH.

41:50.609 --> 41:53.645
I'M SORRY.

