* HIDE BEHIND IT

42:10.662 --> 42:12.698
*

42:12.731 --> 42:14.733
* LET 'EM GO
GIVE IT UP *

42:14.766 --> 42:16.201
SAM LEFT ME.

42:16.234 --> 42:18.737
WHAT A MORON.

42:20.271 --> 42:22.608
TOO SOON.
I'M STILL IN LOVE WITH HER.

42:22.641 --> 42:25.611
